Package net.sf.mmm.client.ui.base.widget.factory Description

Contains the API and default implementations of factories for widgets.

Client UI Base Widget Factory

This package contains the API and default implementations for factories such as UiSingleWidgetButtonFactory or UiSingleWidgetFactory. Please consult Client UI API for an introduction.
